---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();

const links = [
	{ href: "/", label: "作成フォーム" },
	{ href: "/bulk", label: "一括読み込み" },
	{ href: "/guide", label: "使い方" },
	{ href: "/spec", label: "技術仕様" },
];
---

<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-slate-200/60 py-8 text-center">
	<p class="font-heading mb-1 text-lg font-black italic tracking-tighter text-slate-900">
		Thunderbird<span class="text-brand-600"> QR</span>
	</p>
	<p class="mx-auto mb-3 max-w-md text-xs text-slate-400 text-balance">
		This tool is useful for hosting providers and for setting up or deploying company-issued smartphones.
	</p>
	<nav class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2">
		{links.map((link) => (
			<a href={link.href} class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-brand-600">
				{link.label}
			</a>
		))}
	</nav>
	<p class="mb-3 text-xs text-slate-400">
		入力されたメールアカウント情報はブラウザ内でQRコードに変換されるのみで、サーバーへ送信・収集されることはありません。
	</p>
	<p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
		&copy; {year} <a href="https://4y4.app" class="hover:text-brand-600">4y4.app</a>
	</p>
</footer>
